🔹 Preamble to the Laws

These are the foundational commandments of the Agentic Enterprise. They are not best practices; they are laws of physics for the digital workforce. Violate any one of them, and your agentic transformation will fail—often silently, expensively, and at scale. The 40% cancellation rate forecasted by Gartner for 2027 is not a prediction of technological failure; it is a prediction of Law-breaking.

Each Law is presented with its core statement, the strategic imperative, the supporting evidence, and the specific failure mode it prevents.

