The Skeptic's Addendum Integration:

· Arrogant Agent: High Confidence (>80%), Low Accuracy (<50%). Deployment is strictly forbidden. This agent will confidently lie to users and destroy trust.
· Self-Aware Agent: Low Confidence, Low Accuracy. This agent knows it needs help. It is safe to deploy in Shadow Mode (Phase 4) but not Full Production.

Phase 3 Gate

Gate Name: Evaluation Harness Clearance
Requirement: ALL metrics must meet minimum thresholds.
Failure Protocol: Return to Phase 2: BUILD. If the agent cannot meet the 70% success rate after three Build-Evaluate cycles, escalate to Phase 1: DESIGN for workflow decomposition review.

